high_descs: Turn left and face the black table in front of you.
Take the soap from the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink in front of you.
Place the soap in the sink in front of you.
Turn around and face the black table in front of you.
Take the soap from the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink in front of you.
Place the soap in the sink in front of you.
Walk to the tub and turn left to face the black table.
Pick up the bar of soap to the left of the tube.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the soap in sink to the left of the purple rag.
Turn around and walk back over to the black table.
Pick up the bar of soap from the table.
Walk back over to the sink.
Put the bar of soap down in the sink to the right of the rag.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of soap to the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the bath tub ahead of you and turn to your left, then go to the black end table against the wall.
Pick up the bar of soap between the empty toilet paper roll and the other bar of soap.
Turn around and go to the sink across from you.
Place the bar of soap in the sink.
Turn around and go back to the black end table against the wall.
Pick up the bar of soap on the front left corner of the table.
Turn around and go back to the sink.
Place the bar of soap in the sink to the right of the purple wash cloth.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the sink.
